lass=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Information messages (default color)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Processing file...<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">info</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Server configuration loaded<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Error messages (red)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">error</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Failed to connect to database<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">err</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Invalid input provided<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Strong error messages (red background)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">strongError</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Critical system failure!<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Warning messages (yellow)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">warn</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Deprecated function used<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Strong warning messages (yellow background)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">strongWarn</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Memory usage approaching limit<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>);\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// With timestamps</span>\n<span class=\"pl-smi\">Tip</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">error</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\"><span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span>Connection failed<span class=\"pl-pds\">'</span></span>, <span class=\"pl-c1\">true</span>);\n<span class=\"pl-c\">// Output: \"2024/03/15 14:30:25:Connection failed\"</span>\n</code></pre>\n"},"parentId":965}
